---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Stephanie Kay McGennis - Co-Founder & Family Leader"
  description="Meet Stephanie Kay McGennis, co-founder and family leader of the McGennis family in Jefferson City, Missouri. Partner in business and life with Caleb McGennis."
  type="profile"
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20 md:py-32 px-4 border-b border-gray-200">
    <div class="container mx-auto text-center max-w-4xl">
      <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-7xl font-display font-bold mb-8 text-gray-900 leading-tight tracking-tight">
        Stephanie Kay McGennis
      </h1>
      <div class="h-1 w-24 bg-brass-horizontal rounded-full shadow-sm mx-auto mb-8"></div>
      <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-gray-600 mb-4 font-medium">Co-Founder & Family Leader</p>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-500 mb-8 font-light">Partner in Business & Life</p>
      <a href="https://www.facebook.com/stephanie.davis.900388" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="group inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 rounded-xl bg-mcgennis-maroon text-white font-medium tracking-wide hover:bg-opacity-90 transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md">
        Connect on Facebook
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Biography -->
  <section class="py-24 px-4">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="text-5xl font-display font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 tracking-tight">About Stephanie</h2>
      <div class="h-1 w-24 bg-brass-horizontal rounded-full shadow-sm mb-8"></div>
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-6 font-light">
          Stephanie Kay McGennis is the heart and co-founder of the McGennis family enterprise in Jefferson City, Missouri.
          As a dedicated wife, mother, and business partner, Stephanie plays a vital role in the family's success and
          community impact.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-6 font-light">
          Working alongside her husband <a href="/family/caleb" class="text-mcgennis-navy font-medium hover:text-mcgennis-gold transition">Caleb Michael McGennis</a>,
          Stephanie contributes to the family's various business ventures and helps guide their vision for making
          Jefferson City proud.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-500 leading-relaxed font-light">
          As a mother to Leonardo Bryton and Raphael Corwyn, Stephanie balances family life with supporting the
          entrepreneurial endeavors that define the McGennis family legacy in Central Missouri.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Family -->
  <section class="py-24 px-4 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="text-5xl font-display font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 tracking-tight">Family</h2>
      <div class="h-1 w-24 bg-brass-horizontal rounded-full shadow-sm mb-12"></div>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-900 tracking-tight">Husband</h3>
          <a href="/family/caleb" class="group flex items-center gap-4 p-4 bg-gray-50 hover:bg-white transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl hover:border-mcgennis-navy hover:shadow-md">
            <div>
              <p class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 tracking-tight">Caleb Michael McGennis</p>
              <p class="text-gray-500 mb-2 font-light">Entrepreneur & Ministry Leader</p>
              <div class="flex items-center text-mcgennis-navy font-medium group-hover:text-mcgennis-gold transition-colors">
                View Profile →
              </div>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-900 tracking-tight">Sons</h3>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <a href="/family/leonardo" class="group p-6 bg-gray-50 hover:bg-white transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl hover:border-mcgennis-forest hover:shadow-md">
              <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-gray-900 tracking-tight">Leonardo Bryton McGennis</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-500 mb-3 font-light">Eldest son</p>
              <div class="flex items-center text-mcgennis-forest font-medium group-hover:text-mcgennis-gold transition-colors">
                Learn more →
              </div>
            </a>
            <a href="/family/raphael" class="group p-6 bg-gray-50 hover:bg-white transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl hover:border-mcgennis-gold hover:shadow-md">
              <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-gray-900 tracking-tight">Raphael Corwyn McGennis</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-500 mb-3 font-light">Youngest son</p>
              <div class="flex items-center text-mcgennis-gold font-medium group-hover:text-mcgennis-navy transition-colors">
                Learn more →
              </div>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact CTA -->
  <section class="py-24 px-4 bg-white border-t border-gray-200">
    <div class="container mx-auto text-center max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="text-5xl font-display font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900 tracking-tight">Connect With The McGennis Family</h2>
      <div class="h-1 w-24 bg-brass-horizontal rounded-full shadow-sm mx-auto mb-8"></div>
      <p class="text-xl mb-12 text-gray-500 font-light">
        Learn more about our family's journey in Jefferson City, Missouri
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="group inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 rounded-xl bg-mcgennis-maroon text-white font-medium tracking-wide hover:bg-opacity-90 transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md">
        Get In Touch
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SEO Content -->
  <section class="sr-only">
    <h2>Stephanie Kay McGennis - Jefferson City Family Leader</h2>
    <p>
      Stephanie Kay McGennis is the co-founder and family leader of the prominent McGennis family in Jefferson City,
      Missouri. Married to Caleb Michael McGennis, Stephanie is a dedicated mother to Leonardo Bryton McGennis and
      Raphael Corwyn McGennis.
    </p>
    <p>
      As a key partner in the family's business ventures and community initiatives, Stephanie plays an essential role
      in the McGennis family's mission to become Jefferson City's most notable family.
    </p>
    <p>
      Keywords: Stephanie McGennis, Stephanie Kay McGennis, McGennis family Jefferson City, Jefferson City Missouri families,
      Caleb and Stephanie McGennis, McGennis family business, Jefferson City notable families
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
